title: nice house for rent
posting_body: ['Available in October.', ' Nice 4 bedroom, 2 bath house in very nice, well kept neighborhood.', '2 blocks from Johnsville Elementary and also close to middle school and high school.', 'Tiled bathrooms, 6 panel oak doors, newer furnace and air, attached double garage, fenced back', 'yard, deck, shed in back yard.', ' Close to all the stores and businesses along Hwy 65 but far enough', 'away from the noise and traffic.', 'Previous tenants leaving after nearly 10 years because they bought a house.', " I'm a really good", 'landlord and looking for more really good tenants to settle in and make it a long term home for', 'their family.', "I have really thorough professional background checks so if that's a problem please don't waste my", 'time or yours.', 'House is not for sale so please no realtors or flippers.', 'No pets, no smoking.', 'Please reply with your phone number or I will not respond,']
